OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton clean
OL,6,FDeep underground in Brighton and Hove
OL,7,Flies one of the greatest feats of
OL,8,Fengineering in the country.
OL,10,FSouthern Water's "super sewer", which
OL,11,Fwas constructed nearly 15 years ago,
OL,12,Fwas built to tackle water pollution on
OL,13,Fthe iconic beaches.
OL,15,FIt has been so successful the last
OL,16,Frecorded discharge into the sea in the
OL,17,Fcity was in 2012, and Southern Water
OL,18,Fsays it is one example of what it's
OL,19,Fdoing to clean up its act.
