OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton clean
OL,6,FThe sewer is more of a tunnel, which
OL,7,Feffectively holds wastewater, until it
OL,8,Fcan be treated at nearby sewage works.
OL,10,FIt can hold more than 150,000 cubic
OL,11,Fmetres of wastewater, equal to 150,000
OL,12,Ftonnes, during spells of intense
OL,13,Fweather.
OL,15,FSouthern Water told ITV Meridian that
OL,16,Fthe "super sewer" plays a role in
OL,17,Freducing pollution incidents, but the
OL,18,Fdesign isn't the answer for every
OL,19,Flocation.
