OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton clean
OL,6,FBuilding more of these would be
OL,7,Fdamaging to the environment, the
OL,8,Fcompany says, due to the amount of
OL,9,Fmaterials and disruption needed to
OL,10,Fconstruct them.
OL,12,FThey also cost "billions", a spend
OL,13,Fwhich is unsustainable for water
OL,14,Fsuppliers in the UK.
OL,16,FIt's estimated, that if the design was
OL,17,Fto be rolled out across the country,
OL,18,Fit would cost upwards of #600billion.
