OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F411A1722448797
OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton clean
OL,6,F"So for sure these can play part of
OL,7,Fsolving that problem, but they're
OL,8,Fcertainly not the solution."
OL,10,FSouthern Water says it is instead
OL,11,Fexploring other solutions for much of
OL,12,Fits network, and told ITV Meridian it
OL,13,Fis investing heavily to reduce spills
OL,14,Finto our waterways.
OL,16,FInstead of building more "super
OL,17,Fsewers", it is adding additional
OL,18,Fcapacity at treatment works, and
OL,19,Flooking into ways of diverting
OL,20,Frainwater away from the network.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
