OL,6,FSimon added: "We can build extra
OL,7,Fcapacity at our sewage treatment works
OL,8,Fto help attenuate some of those flows
OL,9,Fwhich is what we're doing.
OL,11,F"We're building extra capacity at our
OL,12,Fworks, but again if we can keep the
OL,13,Fwater out that doesn't need those big
OL,14,Fengineering solutions.
