OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton clean
OL,6,F"If we can keep that water out at
OL,7,Fsource that's a vital part of making
OL,8,Fthis work and avoiding that need to
OL,9,Feffectively re-plumb many of these
OL,10,Ftowns and cities that were built in a
OL,11,Fday when it was okay to join up the
OL,12,Ffoul water flows from people's homes
OL,13,Fwith the rain water flows."
OL,15,FSouthern Water's CEO, in an exclusive
OL,16,Finterview with ITV Meridian,
OL,17,Facknowledged the company needed to go
OL,18,Ffurther to tackle discharges.
