OL,6,FHe sat down with Matt Teale, where he
OL,7,Fadmitted that "too much rain" was to
OL,8,Fblame for the record levels of sewage
OL,9,Fdischarges in 2023.
OL,11,FThe company says it has invested
OL,12,F#10billion in the last 30 years to
OL,13,Faddress pollution, and says more will
OL,14,Fbe done to improve infrastructure.
OL,16,FYou can catch the full report on
OL,17,FSouthern Water's 'super sewer' on ITVX.
